{
  "sourceLanguage" : "ja",
  "strings" : {
    "「署名する」を押すと、マイナンバーカードをかざす画面が表示されます。読み取りが終わるまでカードを iPhone の上部に重ねたまま動かさないでください。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Tapping “Sign” opens the card-reading screen. Hold the card against the top of your iPhone and keep it still until reading finishes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@ 〜 %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%1$@ – %2$@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@（%@）" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "%1$@ (%2$@)"
