            "value" : "%lld"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "6文字から16文字の半角英数字で入力してください" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Enter 6 to 16 alphanumeric characters"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "ByteRange" : {

    },
    "JPKI Local Signer" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "JPKI Local Signer"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "JPKI Local Signer は、マイナンバーカードの署名用電子証明書を使い、iPhone 単体で PDF に電子署名を行うオープンソースのツールです。署名処理はすべて端末内で完結し、外部サーバーや事業者を経由しません。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "JPKI Local Signer is an open-source tool that digitally signs PDFs using the signature certificate on your My Number Card, entirely on your iPhone. All signing happens on-device and never passes through external servers or third parties."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "JPKI の判定はアプリ同梱の JPKI ルート証明書（署名用CA 01〜03）との照合によります。その他の認証局はPDF内の証明書チェーンの検証のみで、失効確認（CRL/OCSP）はいずれも行っていません。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The JPKI classification is based on matching against the JPKI root certificates bundled with the app (signature CA 01–03). Other authorities are verified only against the certificate chain embedded in the PDF; revocation (CRL/OCSP) is never checked."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "JPKI（マイナンバーカード）の署名ではありません" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Not a JPKI (My Number Card) signature"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "PDF" : {

    },
    "PDFが選択されていません" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "No PDF selected"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "PDFに埋め込まれた電子署名の値と、署名以降の改ざんの有無を端末内だけで確認します。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Checks the digital signatures embedded in the PDF and whether it was altered after signing — entirely on this device."
          }
        }
      }
    },
