    "キャンセル" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Cancel"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "この PDF には既に %lld 件の署名があります。追加署名は増分更新で付与され、既存の署名は保持されます。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "variations" : {
            "plural" : {
              "one" : {
                "stringUnit" : {
                  "state" : "translated",
                  "value" : "This PDF already contains %lld signature. Your signature will be added as an incremental update; the existing signature is preserved."
                }
              },
              "other" : {
                "stringUnit" : {
                  "state" : "translated",
                  "value" : "This PDF already contains %lld signatures. Your signature will be added as an incremental update; the existing signatures are preserved."
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このPDFが登記オンライン申請の形式要件に適合するかを確認します。署名の有効性の判定とは独立です" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Checks whether this PDF meets the format requirements for MOJ registry online applications. Independent of signature validity"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このPDFをどうしますか" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "What would you like to do with this PDF?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このPDFを検証モードで開きます" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Opens this PDF in verification mode"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このPDFを署名モードで開きます" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Opens this PDF in signing mode"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "このアプリについて" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "About This App"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "この判定は法務省の形式要件（adbe.pkcs7.detached 等）への適合であり、署名の有効性とは独立です。クラウド署名等は署名として有効でも登記形式には適合しません。" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This check covers conformance to the MOJ (Ministry of Justice) format requirements (adbe.pkcs7.detached, etc.) and is independent of signature validity. Cloud-signed PDFs can be valid signatures yet still not conform to the registry format."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "この機能は開発検証用です。実際のマイナンバーカードやNFCは使用せず、ダミーの証明書と署名値でPDF組み立てパイプラインのみを検証します。本番の署名としては使用できません。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This feature is for development testing only. It exercises the PDF assembly pipeline with a dummy certificate and signature value, without a real My Number Card or NFC. It cannot be used for production signatures."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "この環境はNFC読み取りに対応していません。" : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "NFC reading is not available in this environment."
